attributionInfo.agentName: Educators Realty Group Powered By Keller Williams

data.description: Beautiful walk-out basement home sitting on just over 1 acre on a quiet country road. The exterior offers a healthy mix of yard and woods, a water feature in the front, a fenced back yard with an above ground pool and ample room to host all the fun gatherings. Inside you'll find 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms and tons of updates including a new water heater and a/c unit. The main floor boasts a great floorplan, updated white trim and doors, hardwood flooring in the main living area, a stunning stone fireplace in an expansive living room, a large formal dining room with updated lighting and tile floor, and two great guest rooms. The kitchen has tons of storage, great counter space, custom painted cabinetry, tile backsplash and updated appliances. The master is spacious with two large closets, a bay window and boasts an ensuite that allows you to have your own space to relax or get ready for the day. The basement is massive with two large living spaces, a bar set up, and two additional rooms that could easily be converted into a 4th bedroom and a media room. This place is sure to impress and one you don't want to miss!!  Complete with a 1-year Home Warranty.
